{"id": 3000, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得生活中的哪些事物，可以被当成自己的另类“个人史”？", "description": "翻开来的时候，感觉就像生活的年轮。（题图来自：iStock ©️ jossdim）", "record_count": 1321, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190910220948oELuJicAfUPCMhsB.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-09-12T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 348929, "content": "出丑次数过多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667430}, {"id": 346628, "content": "朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1659181}, {"id": 346635, "content": "火车票、飞机票、飞行轨迹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 899902}, {"id": 346383, "content": "读过的书，每一本都或多或少构成了现在的我", "image": null, "praise_count": 332, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474485}, {"id": 346640, "content": "手机便签，简直就是我的碎碎念合集", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662006}, {"id": 346385, "content": "每一件穿过的衣服 ，风格和审美的演变", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661665}, {"id": 346386, "content": "鞋子、照片、眼镜\n去过的地方\n每个deep的彻夜长谈\n朋友对我模糊印象\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 881811}, {"id": 346387, "content": "QQ说说和文章。", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661671}, {"id": 346388, "content": "爱过的人🙈", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952931}, {"id": 346389, "content": "听过的歌，看过的电影，收藏的车票。", "image": null, "praise_count": 201, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655378}, {"id": 346390, "content": "🎵歌单", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661686}, {"id": 346646, "content": "我的字迹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1448335}, {"id": 346392, "content": "朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1495474}, {"id": 346393, "content": "豆瓣", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1495474}, {"id": 346395, "content": "裸睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277552}, {"id": 346396, "content": "她", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1536020}, {"id": 346397, "content": "外号吧，在不同阶段不同地方有不同的外号。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661711}, {"id": 346398, "content": "读的书，接触的人，自己的想法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455065}, {"id": 346401, "content": "手机的截屏。看到能想起来当时的心情和在做的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433119}, {"id": 346402, "content": "豆瓣+穷游", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671570}, {"id": 346403, "content": "日記\n女朋友\n電影偏好\n閱讀偏好\n動漫偏好\n時間表的構成\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786838}, {"id": 346404, "content": "身边的朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657233}, {"id": 346405, "content": "手机相册", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105336}, {"id": 346406, "content": "水杯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640904}, {"id": 346407, "content": "豆瓣读过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378748}, {"id": 346408, "content": "在手机留言簿里写下的所有无意义的话语", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380372}, {"id": 346409, "content": "鞋子变脏的痕迹 用了几年的头像 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462905}, {"id": 346410, "content": "收到过的明信片，在旅行地收集的各种宣传单", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661729}, {"id": 346411, "content": "住过的房间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220766}, {"id": 346412, "content": "认识的每一个人都或多或少的教会了我一些什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661689}, {"id": 346413, "content": "每一张照片，照片里有不同的风景", "image": "img/option/option/20190913145617E5pfBZUqR17GcOQH.jpg", "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661732}, {"id": 346414, "content": "每次去餐厅吃不同的美食，用相机留下记忆！照片里有我，每个不同时期，照片里都有不同的我，不同的眼神，透漏着不同的心境！", "image": "img/option/option/20190913145925ytlGC3FYd5qw9o7K.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661732}, {"id": 346415, "content": "对于我而言，每次穿着新衣服拍照的时候，每次画着不同的妆容，搭配不同的发型的时候，相机一拍便成了永恒，随着岁月的流逝，年老的时候看着自己一张张照片，仿佛每个阶段的故事都在眼前！", "image": "img/option/option/20190913150337FxDNqPOL5EY3bilQ.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661732}, {"id": 346416, "content": "对我个人来说，应该是朋友吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355229}, {"id": 346417, "content": "想办法脱离人群，一个人去做很多事儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293984}, {"id": 346418, "content": "日记本、手机备忘录", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493137}, {"id": 346419, "content": "手机相册\n看到各种因为奇奇怪怪的原因留在手机里的照片一下子想起自己做了什么事😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493137}, {"id": 346420, "content": "曾经的鞋子。走过的路和回忆，也能看出当时的审美和消费水平。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271976}, {"id": 346423, "content": "每年不同的心态，所导致做的不同的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1419514}, {"id": 346424, "content": "豆瓣发言区～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648005}, {"id": 346425, "content": "手机里的相册", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660806}, {"id": 346426, "content": "去过的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566870}, {"id": 346428, "content": "看过的文章，创建的歌单，保存的图片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1624720}, {"id": 346430, "content": "各个阶段的准考证(╹ૅ×╹ૅ)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1658035}, {"id": 346431, "content": "iPhone健身记录里的每一个⭕️", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429599}, {"id": 346432, "content": "去过的地方，阅读过的书，遇见的人，看的电影，个人兴趣爱好变化，一次次三观的解构与重组。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661580}, {"id": 346435, "content": "楼顶上的风景可解不少忧愁", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718332}, {"id": 346436, "content": "喜欢过的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1594602}, {"id": 346438, "content": "文学、电影、音乐、穿衣风格", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499206}, {"id": 347465, "content": "qq空间和我的相册", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664466}]}